## FAQs

### How much does a sound system cost for an event?

The cost of a sound system for an event can vary significantly depending on the size and requirements of your event. At Malaga Event Gear, we offer packages that start as low as $290 for small gatherings and can go up to $650 or more for large scale events with high end equipment.

### What is the most profitable rental item?

The most profitable rental items typically include high demand AV equipment such as projectors, LED screens, and wireless microphones. At Malaga Event Gear, we have observed that items like projection screens and sophisticated sound systems consistently generate significant revenue due to their frequent use in various event types.

### What AV is needed for a conference?

![Modern corporate event setup with large projection screens, round tables, and professional lighting](https://cdn.malagaeventgear.com/blog/1313/corporate-event-100x100.webp)

For a successful conference, essential AV equipment typically includes:

– Projectors and screens  
– Sound systems with microphones (lapel, handheld, or panel)  
– LED or video walls  
– Laptops or tablets for presentations  
– Technical support for live streaming or video conferencing

Malaga Event Gear provides comprehensive AV solutions tailored to the unique needs of conferences.

### Is it cheaper to rent or buy a sound system?

Renting a sound system is usually more cost effective for event specific needs, especially for one time events or when the latest technology is required. It avoids the upfront costs and maintenance associated with purchasing. At Malaga Event Gear, our rental options ensure you get the latest technology at a fraction of the purchase price.

### What are the most rented pieces of equipment?

The most rented pieces of equipment from Malaga Event Gear typically include:

– Wireless microphones  
– PA systems  
– Projectors and screens  
– LED video walls  
– Stage lighting

These items are crucial in delivering engaging and seamless events.

